<section id="map" style="height:400px;">

  <%= render 'shared/contact_map' %>

</section>

<section id="info">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-7 message">
        <h3>We're so confident you'll enroll with us, we'll fly you here for free!</h3>

        <p>
          We are pleased you have chosen to visit our campus.  <strong>Over 70% of our visitors enroll in our program.</strong>
          Complete the form below to get a taste of what our groundbreaking college-core program is all about.
        </p>

        <p>
          Campus visits can happen on any Monday, Wednesday or Friday throughout our calendar year (as long as our offices are open).
          We like to have you arrive the night before and catch a return flight late afternoon the following day.
          If you have any questions or special requests, please use the <em>special requests</em> field below.
          We will do our best to accommodate you. An admissions counselor will contact you with a sample itinerary and
          more details before booking a final flight.  We are so excited to have you visit our campus.
          It is a joy sharing this program with you!
        </p>

        <%= render 'form' %>
      </div>

      <aside class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 contact">

        <%= render 'shared/contact_sidebar' %>

      </aside>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
